        "synopsis": {
            "value": "In the midst of a fight against drug trafficking, Kwanruetai, the kind daughter of a noble family, meets Major Dr. Chatklao Juthathep, a military doctor. Despite their growing love, Kwanruetai is torn due to her family’s long-standing feud with the Juthatheps, caused by her mother’s past heartbreak. As Kwanruetai grapples with the past and her feelings, Chatklao remains determined to win her heart. Will love overcome their families' conflict, or are they\n\ndoomed to remain apart?",
            "source": "mydramalist",
